

09/26/2022 - Test Cases 1

SDLC

AGILE AND WATERFALL

SCRUM - 

User Story - As a user, I should be able to login

Components of the user story

	1. Summary, title - As a user, I should be able to login

	2. Acceptance Criteria - 
	    Users should be able to log in with the valid credentials

		Users should get the error message with the incorrect username.

		The user should get the error message with the incorrect password.

		Users should navigate to the dashboard page when login successful

		User can longin only after the captcha validation

		Two factor authentications

		Forget password options

		Remember new device functionality

User story has summary and acceptance criteria ( requirement, scenarios) to be able be accepted by the client and users. 


Syntax of:
-----------
User Story: As a user, I should be able to login

Acceptance Criteria: Users should be able to log in with the valid credentials

Test Scenario: User should be able to log in with the valid credentials (Validate that user is able to login with valid credentials)

Test Case: Validate that user is able to login with valid credentials




























